title: Pink Floyd Discogrphy
description:
Here is the full discography for Oink Floyd.  My idea of a full discography is all studio albums and compilation albums, and all soundtrack songs.  No bootlegs, etc. They are all MP3 VBR192.  They sound great. If you want better quality go elsewhere. Trolling will get you nowhere.  And they are FREE!  All nicely tagged, with artwork. That being said here is what you get:

The Piper At The Gates Of Dawn
A Saucerful Of Secrets
More
Ummagumma
Atom Heart Mother
Mettle
Obscured By Clouds
The Dark Side Of The Moon
Wish You Were Here
Animals
The Wall
The Final Cut
A Momentary apse Of Reason
The Division Bell
The Endless River

A note about the The Dark Side Of The Moon.  I combined the tracks Brain Damage/Eclipse and Speak To Me/Breathe. THose tracks should always be played together in my opinion.  Some will like it some not so much.  It is what it is.

So please enjoy, share and leave feedback!
